article.description: — Marcus Shaver Jr. registered 17 points as Boise State narrowly beat Tulsa 63-58 on Friday night.
article.headline: Shaver Jr. scores 17 to carry Boise State over Tulsa 63-58
article.linkText: Shaver Jr. scores 17 to carry Boise State over Tulsa 63-58
article.story: BOISE, Idaho -- — Marcus Shaver Jr. registered 17 points as Boise State narrowly beat Tulsa 63-58 on Friday night. Abu Kigab had 17 points for Boise State (4-4). Emmanuel Akot added 12 points. Tyson Degenhart had 11 points. Jeriah Horne had 17 points for the Golden Hurricane (4-4). Sam Griffin added 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
